03:20:23.650 --> 03:20:24.712
Let it be permanent.

03:20:25.874 --> 03:20:26.796
Let it be permanent.

03:20:27.877 --> 03:20:28.899
Let it all go.

03:20:29.540 --> 03:20:33.708
Be permanent, Lord, in the mighty name of Jesus.

03:20:34.389 --> 03:20:35.811
And everybody said, amen.

03:20:37.334 --> 03:20:38.576
Your amen is very weak.

03:20:40.900 --> 03:20:42.263
Say a stronger amen.

03:20:44.847 --> 03:20:48.754
And give the Lord your loudest clap and shout of victory.

03:20:58.754 --> 03:20:59.755
You are victorious.

03:21:01.257 --> 03:21:02.159
You have overcome.

03:21:03.581 --> 03:21:05.824
I declare over you, you have overcome.

03:21:07.126 --> 03:21:08.748
I say, you have overcome.

03:21:10.110 --> 03:21:13.815
That thing that you've never overcome, it has been overcome today.

03:21:14.937 --> 03:21:23.328
By the blood, by the blood, by the blood, by the blood, by the blood, by the blood.

03:21:24.209 --> 03:21:27.474
You have the victory in Jesus' name.

03:21:28.450 --> 03:21:31.534
Give two people a victorious hike and take your seats.

03:21:32.996 --> 03:21:34.218
Tell them you're victorious.

03:21:37.001 --> 03:21:38.083
Tell them you're victorious.

03:21:40.306 --> 03:21:41.467
Tell them you're victorious.

03:21:43.290 --> 03:21:45.132
And take your seat in his presence.

03:21:47.636 --> 03:21:48.116
Beautiful.

03:21:52.522 --> 03:21:53.183
God bless you.

03:21:54.304 --> 03:21:55.746
Did you tell somebody God bless you?

03:21:56.988 --> 03:21:58.450
Tell somebody God bless you.

03:21:59.650 --> 03:22:03.554
Believe it as you say, say to the person, God bless you.

03:22:05.996 --> 03:22:10.601
You are releasing a weapon and a power into the person's life.

03:22:11.081 --> 03:22:15.185
Look the person in the eyes and say, God bless you.

03:22:20.050 --> 03:22:21.492
You don't easily come by blessings.

03:22:24.074 --> 03:22:26.497
People say good morning, good afternoon, good evening.

03:22:26.537 --> 03:22:28.018
They say hello, mate.

03:22:30.306 --> 03:22:31.408
These are the things you hear.

03:22:32.109 --> 03:22:34.193
You don't easily hear God bless you.

03:22:36.037 --> 03:22:36.898
Hello, hi.

03:22:38.321 --> 03:22:39.042
Good morning.

03:22:39.103 --> 03:22:39.563
How are you?

03:22:39.604 --> 03:22:41.527
It doesn't bring blessings.

03:22:42.629 --> 03:22:47.418
So tell somebody again, God bless you.

03:22:51.125 --> 03:22:53.650
Look for somebody else and release another blessing.

03:22:59.490 --> 03:23:02.132
Look for somebody else and release a blessing.

03:23:07.277 --> 03:23:09.700
Tell the blessing you needed for the week.

03:23:10.120 --> 03:23:11.561
God bless you.

03:23:16.866 --> 03:23:17.827
You shall be favored.

03:23:19.869 --> 03:23:20.790
You shall be helped.

03:23:22.191 --> 03:23:23.272
You shall be promoted.

03:23:24.594 --> 03:23:26.315
You will increase and not decrease.

03:23:27.837 --> 03:23:29.138
You will be victorious.

03:23:30.210 --> 03:23:31.572
It will be well with you.

03:23:33.113 --> 03:23:35.476
God wipes every tear from your face.

03:23:36.817 --> 03:23:38.359
God gives you laughter.

03:23:39.340 --> 03:23:40.702
God gives you a dance.

03:23:41.823 --> 03:23:44.246
God gives you a reason to celebrate.

03:23:45.387 --> 03:23:47.709
Receive it.

03:23:47.730 --> 03:23:48.831
Receive it.

03:23:49.752 --> 03:23:51.013
Receive it.

03:23:52.154 --> 03:23:53.116
God bless you.

03:23:53.716 --> 03:23:55.378
Put your hands together one more time.

03:23:57.474 --> 03:24:00.177
Wow, what an amazing service that was.

